  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong>:</p><ul><li>lead the tendering process</li><li>prepare tender documentation</li><li>submit quotation or tender document</li><li>estimate construction cost in competitive manner</li><li>monitor monthly progress</li><li>process claims and contractual payment</li><li>negotiate and award sub-contractors</li><li>attend site meeting and assist supervisors in letter/report writing and corresponding contract issues</li><li>responsible in preparing documentation including daily report, monthly progress report, method of statement and work procedure to project manager.</li><li>order paint materials correctly and follow up with the delivery status</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><ul><li>degree in quantity surveyor or equivalent</li><li>at least 3 years of working experience in the construction industry</li><li>good in English communication, must be confident on talking to clients and suppliers!</li><li>good in attitude and must be willing to learn.</li><li>at least 1 years' working experience in SG as a QS!</li></ul>",
